            "title": "通用汽車計畫將別克昂科威的生產從中國轉移到堪薩斯州",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"通用汽車計畫將別克昂科威的生產從中國轉移到堪薩斯州\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/PdQyQoQMSS3zisQ5Bl04Rg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/d9c0e940-9908-11ed-9dff-100ab0a99a0e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">通用汽車計畫將別克昂科威的生產從中國轉移到堪薩斯州</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
