        {
            "title": "英特爾在盤後交易中大跌 營收預期平淡且CEO稱在努力應對生產問題",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/eI2Oa0HQQI7a8DQm5JwHTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/c7520f7b9d43267088ea098a4718e69a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:英特爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/英特爾\">英特爾</a>股價在盤後交易中一度重挫13%，執行長<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:陳立武;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/陳立武\">陳立武</a>給出的預期平平，並警告稱這家晶片製造商在應對生產問題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對第一季度的營收和盈利預期均遠低於華爾街預測。在與分析師的電話會議上，陳立武表示公司需要「時間和決心」才能扭轉局面，此番言論導致股價進一步下跌。生產環節的障礙阻礙了公司復甦，令原本期待新產品能帶來更大提振的投資者感到失望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們處於一個多年發展階段，」執行長表示。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"英特爾執行長陳立武表示，公司需要改進製造工藝。攝影：Annabelle Chih/ 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/k9s5VTkSL1UkXD.cYhiL6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/aef4cd43968b83a44026d7621a408060\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">英特爾執行長陳立武表示，公司需要改進製造工藝。攝影：Annabelle Chih/ 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英特爾正面臨製造良率低的困境——即工廠生產的可用晶片比例，這導致其更難完成訂單。該公司多年來一直試圖重振技術優勢，並彌補市場占有率的損失，而這無疑是又一次挫折。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-5132eb9a-235e-3da8-ba61-661e323c9eed-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">陳立武在接受採訪時表示，需求「相當強勁」，公司正在努力解決生產問題。但他同時指出，英特爾在第四季度消耗了大部分庫存。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們的產量和生產製造水平沒有達到我的標準，」陳立武說。「我們需要改進這一點。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著電話會議進行，英特爾股價在盤後交易中一度跌至47.25美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示，第一季度營收預計在117億美元至127億美元之間。該區間的中值低於分析師此前預測的126億美元。該公司預計，不計特定項目，每股純益將實現盈虧平衡。華爾街此前預測該公司每股純益為8美分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第四季度，營收下降4.1%至137億美元。不計部分項目，每股純益為0.15美元。據彭博匯編的數據，分析師此前估計銷售額為134億美元，平均每股純益為9美分。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">經調整後，季度毛利率為37.9%。預計當前財季這一關鍵盈利指標將收縮至34.5%。英特爾鼎盛時期時，其毛利率通常超過60%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Intel Tumbles After CEO Manufacturing Snags Bedevil Comeback</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Edward Ludlow、Katie Greifeld、Romaine Bostick.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E7%89%B9%E7%88%BE%E5%9C%A8%E7%9B%A4%E5%BE%8C%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%B7%8C-%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E5%B9%B3%E6%B7%A1%E4%B8%94ceo%E7%A8%B1%E5%9C%A8%E5%8A%AA%E5%8A%9B%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C-233816842.html",
